description._content: Collection: McCardle (Mrs. W. H.) Photograph Collection Call number: PI/1985.0017 System ID: 77182. Link to the catalog "Confederate Dead." Carte-de-visite composite of individual identified Confederate Generals killed in Civil War: W. O. B. Branch, Earl Van Dorn, J. H. Morgan, W. Barksdale, A. S. Johnston, J. E. B. Stuart, Stonewall Jackson, J. S. Bowen, Zollicoffer, L. Tilghman, A. J. Jenkins, Ben McCullough, Leonidas Polk, and G. J. Rains. Photographer: E. & H. T. Anthony Please see our profile page for information on ordering. Scanned as TIFF in 2010/10/01 by MDAH. Credit: Courtesy of the Mississippi Department of Archives and History
